data.description: Classic two-story home with a charming facade, boasting 3 cozy bedrooms, 1 spacious bath, and a total of 1105 sq ft, perfect for a comfortable and inviting living space for a first time home buyer, and/or an investment property. This home is very well maintained with a spacious kitchen. New features to include new light fixtures, new laminate flooring, newer carpet, freshly painted, new concrete driveway, new concrete walkway and new front concrete steps leading to a huge covered front porch for relaxation. The front yard is tastefully landscaped and a most desired  chainlink fencing that offers a pedestrian gate and a sliding car entry gate for extra security. Can't forget the spacious huge back yard with plenty of room for your fun outdoor activities. Close to shops, grocery stores, and easy access to Hwy 99.
